author: Dr15Jones
body:
This module HTMHTAnalyzer has never worked since the CMSSW_7_0 when it was converted to a DQMEDAnalyzer from a helper class of the now defunct JetMETAnalyzer. Then analyze method did not match the DQMEDAnalyzer base class and therefore would never be called.

This works around the clang warning about the analyze method.
title: Removed HTMHTAnalyzer
